{
  "texts": [
    "Consistency in the experimental setup and data collection methods is maintained throughout this investigation.",
    "The feature extraction process involves MFCCs, and eight other main feature extraction methods are employed to extract the most significant attributes from the dataset.",
    "Our methodology utilized a combination of ML and DL models to tackle the multi-classification problem in detecting heart disease.",
    "This investigation initially utilized the PASCAL classifying heart sound challenge Dataset and the 2016 PhysioNet/Computing in Cardiology (CinC) Challenge datasets.",
    "Ventricular Septal Defect (VSD), Atrial Septal Defect (ASD), Patent Ductus Arteriosus (PDA), murmur, and extrasystole are just a few of the disorders covered by the databases."
  ]
}